# Tab Navigator - Seamless Tab History Navigation

Navigate through your tab history effortlessly with keyboard shortcuts. Like browser page navigation, but for tabs.

## Features:
- Use **Ctrl+Left** and **Ctrl+Right** to navigate tab history.
- Customize shortcuts via `chrome://extensions/shortcuts`.
- Persist tab history across sessions (partial support).
- Lightweight, runs silently in the background.

## Privacy & Security:
- Data stored locally, no external connections or tracking.
- Open source: [GitHub](https://github.com/alexlvcom/tab-navigator)

Ideal for developers, researchers, and power users managing multiple tabs.
